---
import DocsLayout from '../../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro'
---
<DocsLayout title="Autoplay Plugin">
  <h1>Autoplay</h1>
  <p class="lead">Auto-advances slides on a timed interval. Supports pause on hover, pause or disable on user interaction, reverse direction, and page-visibility awareness.</p>

  <h2>Import</h2>
  <pre><code>import {"{"} autoplay {"}"} from '@andresclua/sliderkit-plugins'</code></pre>

  <h2>Options</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Option</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>delay</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>3000</code></td><td>Interval in milliseconds between automatic slide advances.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>pauseOnHover</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>true</code></td><td>Pause autoplay while the pointer is over the slider container.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>pauseOnInteraction</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>true</code></td><td>Pause temporarily after a drag or touch, then resume once the transition ends.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>disableOnInteraction</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>false</code></td><td>Permanently stop autoplay after the first user drag or touch interaction.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>reverseDirection</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>false</code></td><td>Advance to the previous slide instead of the next on each tick.</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>resetOnVisibility</code></td><td><code>boolean</code></td><td><code>true</code></td><td>Stop the interval when the page becomes hidden and restart when it becomes visible again.</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Programmatic control</h2>
  <p>The plugin instance exposes <code>start()</code> and <code>stop()</code> methods.</p>

  <h2>Example</h2>
  <pre><code>{`import { createSlider } from '@andresclua/sliderkit'
import { autoplay } from '@andresclua/sliderkit-plugins'

const ap = autoplay({ delay: 4000, pauseOnHover: true })

createSlider('#my-slider', {
  loop: true,
  plugins: [ap],
})

// Programmatic control
ap.stop()
ap.start()`}</code></pre>

  <p><a href="/demos/autoplay">View autoplay demo</a></p>
</DocsLayout>
